    public abstract class ITInfrastructureOMASAPIResponse
extends FFDCResponseBase
    ITInfrastructureOMASAPIResponse provides a common header for IT Infrastructure OMAS managed rest to its REST API. It manages information about exceptions. If no exception has been raised exceptionClassName is null.
